  rcases h.subset_ball x with ‚ü®R, hR‚ü©,
  refine (bounded_iff_subset_ball x).2 ‚ü®R + Œ¥, _‚ü©,
  assume y hy,
  rcases (mem_thickening_iff _ _).1 hy with ‚ü®z, zE, hz‚ü©,
  calc dist y x ‚â§ dist z x + dist y z : by { rw add_comm, exact dist_triangle _ _ _ }
  ... ‚â§ R + Œ¥ : add_le_add (hR zE) hz.le
end

end thickening --section

